{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"author":{"name":"Kingso","contacts":{"twitter":"#"}},"disqusShortname":"kingsoblog","subtitle":"Kingso's blog","title":"Kingso's blog","url":"https://kingso.netlify.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9b156901-99f0-517c-858a-9305f4e3b42d","html":"<br>\n<h2 id=\"02-js-and-css-clock\"><a href=\"#02-js-and-css-clock\" aria-label=\"02 js and css clock permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>02. JS and CSS Clock</h2>\n<p>현재 시간에 대해 시,분,초침으로 나타내는 시계를 표현한다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"목표\"><a href=\"#%EB%AA%A9%ED%91%9C\" aria-label=\"목표 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>목표</h3>\n<p>1.transform, transition 속성 등을 이용해서 시,분,초침의 위치를 설정한다.</p>\n<p>2.현재의 시,분,초에 대해 각도를 계산하여 변형을 적용시키는 함수 생성.</p>\n<p>3.1초에 한 번씩 2번의 함수가 호출되도록 한다.</p>\n<br>\n<h5 id=\"css-transform-origin--transform-속성\"><a href=\"#css-transform-origin--transform-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"css transform origin  transform 속성 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS transform-origin / transform 속성</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>[ transform-origin ]\n: 원점의 위치를 지정</p>\n<ul>\n<li>left 0% / center 50% / right 100% / top 0% / bottom 100%</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>[ transform ]\n: 요소에 적용할 변형을 지정 (ex. rotate(90deg) )</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h5 id=\"css-transition--transition-timing-function-속성\"><a href=\"#css-transition--transition-timing-function-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"css transition  transition timing function 속성 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS transition / transition-timing-function 속성</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>[ transition ]\n: 속성을 서서히 변화시키는 속성</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>[ transition-timing-function ]\n: transition의 진행 속도를 조절할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>cubic-bezier( n, n, n, n ) : 점을 움직여서 원하는 커브를 만들고, 상단에 있는 수를 사용합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h5 id=\"setinterval-메소드-주기적인-실행\"><a href=\"#setinterval-%EB%A9%94%EC%86%8C%EB%93%9C-%EC%A3%BC%EA%B8%B0%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B8-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-label=\"setinterval 메소드 주기적인 실행 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>setInterval 메소드 (주기적인 실행)</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>일정한 시간 간격으로 작업을 수행하기 위해서 사용</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>setInterval(setDate, 1000); // 1000ms(1초) 간격으로 setDate() 함수를 호출</p>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Javascript30-02/","tagSlugs":["/tag/javascript-30/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-07-16T14:00:00.169Z","description":"JS and CSS Clock","tags":["Javascript30"],"title":"Javascript30 - 02"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/Javascript30-02/"}}